1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,183
Welcome to this unblending practice.

2
00:00:02,183 --> 00:00:07,873
In IFS, blending happens when a part’s
feelings, thoughts, or impulses feel like

3
00:00:07,873 --> 00:00:09,242
all of who you are.

4
00:00:09,242 --> 00:00:13,686
Unblending means creating a little space
so you can relate to the part instead of

5
00:00:13,686 --> 00:00:15,186
being completely inside it.

6
00:00:15,186 --> 00:00:19,874
You might imagine the feeling as a cloud
in the sky of your awareness. It can

7
00:00:19,874 --> 00:00:23,267
still be present, but it does not have to
be all of you.

8
00:00:35,267 --> 00:00:35,267
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

9
00:00:35,267 --> 00:00:37,450
You do not have to push any part away.

10
00:00:37,450 --> 00:00:39,679
We are simply practicing space.

11
00:00:39,679 --> 00:00:41,397
Begin by settling.

12
00:00:41,397 --> 00:00:43,208
Let your body be supported.

13
00:00:43,208 --> 00:00:45,576
Take a slow breath in.

14
00:00:54,576 --> 00:00:54,576
<break time="3s" />

15
00:00:54,576 --> 00:00:55,923
And breathe out.

16
00:00:55,923 --> 00:00:59,638
Now notice what part of you feels most
present right now.

17
00:00:59,638 --> 00:01:00,799
It might be anxious.

18
00:01:00,799 --> 00:01:01,356
Critical.

19
00:01:01,356 --> 00:01:01,913
Numb.

20
00:01:01,913 --> 00:01:02,656
Angry.

21
00:01:02,656 --> 00:01:03,306
Sad.

22
00:01:03,306 --> 00:01:03,910
Driven.

23
00:01:03,910 --> 00:01:04,560
Avoidant.

24
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:05,582
Overwhelmed.

25
00:01:05,582 --> 00:01:06,929
Or something else.

26
00:01:06,929 --> 00:01:09,437
Choose one part to gently focus on.

27
00:01:09,437 --> 00:01:12,456
Not the most overwhelming one if that
feels like too much.

28
00:01:12,456 --> 00:01:14,824
Just one part that is available to
notice.

29
00:01:14,824 --> 00:01:15,985
Now ask:

30
00:01:27,985 --> 00:01:27,985
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

31
00:01:27,985 --> 00:01:30,911
Where do I notice this part in or around
my body?

32
00:01:42,911 --> 00:01:42,911
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

33
00:01:42,911 --> 00:01:44,072
Maybe in the chest.

34
00:01:44,072 --> 00:01:44,722
The throat.

35
00:01:44,722 --> 00:01:45,511
The stomach.

36
00:01:45,511 --> 00:01:46,254
The jaw.

37
00:01:46,254 --> 00:01:47,043
The shoulders.

38
00:01:47,043 --> 00:01:47,832
The head.

39
00:01:47,832 --> 00:01:49,179
The hands.

40
00:01:49,179 --> 00:01:51,362
Or maybe it feels outside the body.

41
00:01:51,362 --> 00:01:52,430
Now ask:

42
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:04,430
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

43
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:07,774
How blended am I with this part from zero
to ten?

44
00:02:19,774 --> 00:02:19,774
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

45
00:02:19,774 --> 00:02:22,746
Zero means you feel completely separate
from it.

46
00:02:22,746 --> 00:02:24,743
Ten means it feels like all of you.

47
00:02:24,743 --> 00:02:26,415
Just notice the number.

48
00:02:26,415 --> 00:02:28,598
Now gently say to this part:

49
00:02:28,598 --> 00:02:30,548
I see that you’re here.

50
00:02:30,548 --> 00:02:32,824
I know you may be trying to help.

51
00:02:32,824 --> 00:02:34,217
I’m not trying to get rid of you.

52
00:02:34,217 --> 00:02:37,189
I would like to understand you from a
little more space.

53
00:02:37,189 --> 00:02:38,350
Now ask the part:

54
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:50,350
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

55
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:53,322
Would you be willing to give me just a
little space?

56
00:03:05,322 --> 00:03:05,322
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

57
00:03:05,322 --> 00:03:06,344
Notice what happens.

58
00:03:24,344 --> 00:03:24,344
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

59
00:03:24,344 --> 00:03:27,038
If the part says no, that is okay.

60
00:03:27,038 --> 00:03:27,781
Ask:

61
00:03:27,781 --> 00:03:30,567
What are you afraid would happen if you
gave me space?

62
00:03:42,567 --> 00:03:42,567
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

63
00:03:42,567 --> 00:03:43,774
Listen gently.

64
00:03:43,774 --> 00:03:47,489
If the part is willing to give space,
notice whether it moves.

65
00:03:47,489 --> 00:03:48,836
Maybe it steps back.

66
00:03:48,836 --> 00:03:50,090
Maybe it softens.

67
00:03:50,090 --> 00:03:51,855
Maybe it becomes less intense.

68
00:03:51,855 --> 00:03:53,527
Maybe nothing changes.

69
00:03:53,527 --> 00:03:55,431
All of that is okay.

70
00:03:55,431 --> 00:03:57,056
Now ask again:

71
00:04:09,056 --> 00:04:09,056
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

72
00:04:09,056 --> 00:04:13,096
How blended do I feel with this part now,
from zero to ten?

73
00:04:25,096 --> 00:04:25,096
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

74
00:04:25,096 --> 00:04:28,115
If the number changed even a little,
notice that.

75
00:04:28,115 --> 00:04:32,155
If it did not change, that is still
useful information.

76
00:04:32,155 --> 00:04:35,127
Now see if you can feel any Self-energy
toward this part.

77
00:04:35,127 --> 00:04:36,613
Maybe curiosity.

78
00:04:36,613 --> 00:04:38,053
Maybe compassion.

79
00:04:38,053 --> 00:04:39,214
Maybe patience.

80
00:04:39,214 --> 00:04:41,908
Maybe simply the willingness to keep
listening.

81
00:04:41,908 --> 00:04:42,837
Ask the part:

82
00:04:54,837 --> 00:04:54,837
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

83
00:04:54,837 --> 00:04:56,184
What do you want me to know?

84
00:05:08,184 --> 00:05:08,184
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

85
00:05:08,184 --> 00:05:08,788
And:

86
00:05:08,788 --> 00:05:10,413
What are you trying to protect me from?

87
00:05:22,413 --> 00:05:22,413
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

88
00:05:22,413 --> 00:05:25,339
Thank the part for showing you whatever
it showed you.

89
00:05:25,339 --> 00:05:27,893
Even if you do not understand it fully
yet.

90
00:05:27,893 --> 00:05:28,682
You might say:

91
00:05:37,682 --> 00:05:37,682
<break time="3s" />

92
00:05:37,682 --> 00:05:39,911
I am learning how to be with you.

93
00:05:39,911 --> 00:05:41,026
We can go slowly.

94
00:05:41,026 --> 00:05:42,791
You do not have to carry this alone.

95
00:05:42,791 --> 00:05:44,556
Now let your attention widen.

96
00:05:44,556 --> 00:05:46,042
Feel your whole body.

97
00:05:46,042 --> 00:05:47,064
Feel the room.

98
00:05:47,064 --> 00:05:49,525
Feel the support underneath you.

99
00:06:01,525 --> 00:06:01,525
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

100
00:06:01,525 --> 00:06:03,383
Take one final breath in.

101
00:06:03,383 --> 00:06:04,544
And let it out.

102
00:06:04,544 --> 00:06:07,238
When you are ready, return.

103
00:06:07,238 --> 00:06:11,214
Even a small amount of space is
meaningful. You are practicing the

104
00:06:11,214 --> 00:06:15,619
difference between being taken over by a
part and being with a part. That

105
00:06:15,619 --> 00:06:18,616
difference is one doorway back to
Self-leadership.

106
00:06:18,616 --> 00:06:23,214
------------------------------------------
------------------------------.

